body_html:
Hi,
I want to use the profiler, by following
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/profiler/README.md
but there is no tf.contrib.tfprof.ProfileContext() anymore in r1.3
and there's no ProfileContext in tf.profiler also.
Can you please fix this? Thanks

maybe try with #12495
